{"tid":803672,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(已出)焼きたて!! ジャぱん日式麵包王作者疑似打著助手的旗號C94推出了女主角梓川月乃同人本","createTime":"2018-09-02T12:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T04:35:09.000Z","uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfa1f5b5b0116a35d132f1eca24d89f0bab7063","tid":803672,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/203530_e47f2ef0d438c314ec03775002c4dc5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F203530_e47f2ef0d438c314ec03775002c4dc5c.jpg&h=b33940e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在C94第二天《日式麵包王》漫畫作者橋口隆志疑似打著自己助手的旗號，推出了《日式麵包王》女主角梓川月乃的全彩R18同人本<br />\n<br />\n「同人」這個概念是個好東西，不是說不是官方做的就叫同人，同人基本概念是「做給志同道合愛好者看的非商業創作」，所以有些參與商業作品的官方畫師也會推出自己參與作品的同人本<br />\n今天C94第二天《日式麵包王》作者橋口隆志也出攤，推出了自己創作的《日式麵包王》R18全彩同人本<br />\n<br />\n[Hassystant] Tsukitate!! Ou-sama Game (Yakitate!! Japan) [Chinese] [基德漢化組]<br />\n<br />\n[ハシスタント] 突きたて!! 王様げぇむ (焼きたて!! ジャぱん)"},{"pid":"86ddf3953fdf789d5e94472c2907689210210b22","tid":803672,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:37:25.000Z","msg":"@%@#%^@#^&amp;@$&amp;@&amp;#*#$*U$^"},{"pid":"75ce32999af2d47a32f147713436468d8a25cb25","tid":803672,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"日式麵包王作者疑借助手名出18禁同人本"},{"pid":"1219964b495f278053462f51fade6eb0a7b16355","tid":803672,"uid":159916,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"黑人who.gif"},{"pid":"34246c2f7cf87ba445fda3928e677784b7684f0a","tid":803672,"uid":54232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"求link"},{"pid":"4008a7dd2f9c9cae1af820677d393c0fb2c8adb1","tid":803672,"uid":34383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"諗起月乃光頭 點j得落"},{"pid":"dbadcaff761be0260f77a2dd85360736